featured_reviews.review_id: This one located at Amreli district was founded by SAIYED DILAWAR CHISHTI (R.A.) who was a very pious diety and in his life has blessed all of his disciples. He passed away on 14th OCTOBER 2018 leaving his disciples under the roof of his two beloved and pious sons, SAIYED JILANIBAPU CHISHTI AND SAIYED NIZAMUDDINBAPU CHISHTI. This masjid was his dream and was fulfilled by the blessing of the almighty, the variance in the colours and chandeliers inside are th ones to be appreciated with provision of all amenities for the prayer goers. May Allah (S.W.T.) bless him for all his deeds and may his soul rest in peace
